	<h1 class="title">为了显得更有男子气概，男人们可能有哪些偏执的信念｜好奇心人类学</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/101671/small/101671.jpg?1455867778" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">潘姜汐熹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-12 13:03:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20580/medium/20580.jpg?1452573527" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="20580" data-title="《为了显得更有男子气概，男人们可能有哪些偏执的信念｜好奇心人类学》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20580/medium/20580.jpg?1452573527" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20580.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
